high_descs: Turn around then go straight to the right side of the dresser
Pick up the CD on the edge of the dresser

high_descs: Turn around and go to the dresser that is directly behind you.
Pick up the CD that is on the dresser.
With the CD in hand turn to your left and go to the white safe that is on the floor.
Open the safe and place the CD in it.  Shut the door.
Turn around and walk to the right side of the dresser.
Pick up the CD to the right of the glass bowl.
Turn left and walk to the front of the white safe.
Open the safe door, place the CD inside of it, close the safe door.
anns.task_desc: To move a CD from the desk to a safe.

Open the vault, place the CD in it, and close the vault.
